summary: Dark home for a common assassin fit with everything you need for your skyrim experience
descriptionHtml:
Fenland Estate is a dark home made for the common assassin. The house mainly looks better at night and has multiple buildings with different purposes.
Its located in between Solitude Saw mill and Dragon Bridge (should be a fast travel marker). Throughout exploring the house the player finds a key and a note revealing that there is a treasure deep within the Estate.Thanks for Downloading and enjoy your new house :)

[Requirements]
Vanilla Skyrim

[Location]
Near Solitude Saw Mill

[Includes]
Assassin armor (with finishing the riddle)
Alchemy shack
Enchanting area
Mines
Armory
Secret Hot spring caves
Docks
Gardens
Library
Crafting Patio
Main House (bed location)

[Problems]
Mannequins in armory may wander

[Quest Spoiles]
Final Key is at the top of the Throat of the world
